headline: T. Rowe Price's AUM Climbs 6.9% in 1H 2025: What's Driving Growth?
summary: TROW AUM rose 6.9% in 1H 2025 to $1.68T, fueled by market gains and inflows into fixed income, multi-asset and alternatives.

headline: Rallying Strong: Avantis ETF Touches 52-Week High with Room to Run
summary: The Avantis International Small Cap Value ETF just hit its 47th new 52-week high in the past 12 months. Up 24% over the past year, the ETF should make patient investors money over the next 3-5 years. Here’s why.
